quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"Nditsuba khulukulu lwa Tur (olwa Nyasaye yalomalomiliakho omurumwa Musa)."
  52,2,"Nende khushitabu shiahandikwa."
  52,3,"Khuliseelo liabambulwa."
  52,4,"Nende khunzu yombakhwa (ya abamalaika balamilangamwo mwikulu)."
  52,5,"Nende khushitsafu shiachingulwa (likulu lili eshitsafu shie eshialo)."
  52,6,"Nende khunyanza yetsula (omulilo)."
  52,7,"Toto eshinyasio shia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shilibaho (khubakhayi)."
  52,8,"Abulaho ulishiikalila tawe."
  52,9,"Inyanga yelikulu lilirenga okhurenga khwene."
  52,10,"Ne efikulu lwa filikhulukha nifichenda okhuchenda khwa toto."
  52,11,"Eshinyasio eshikhongo inyanga eyo shiliba khubayingani."
  52,12,"Balia babayanga mumakhuwa kobusilu."
  52,13,"Inyanga yabaliluumwa mumulilo okhulumwa okhutinyu."
  52,14,"Baliboolelwa mbu: “Kuno nikwo omulilo kwa mwaingananga."
  52,15,"Koo, buno ni obulosi nohomba shimulolangasa tawe?"
  52,16,"Injilemwo, mwisumirisie nohomba mukhaye okhwisumirisia, ninashilalasa khwinywe. Toto enywe murungungwa sa kamwakholanga."""
  52,17,"Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda chomwikulu nende mubwokholo."
  52,18,"Nibasangalila khuka Nyasaye wabu Omulesi abahele, ne Nyasaye wabu Omulesi alibahonokosia okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiomulilo."
  52,19,"“Lie, ne nywe mumwikhoyo khukalia kamwakholanga.”"
  52,20,"Ne baliyeekha khubifumbi bwioluyali, bilondokhane khulunyaali, ne khulibabashila abakhana bomwikulu (Hurul ain)."
  52,21,"Ne balia basuubila mana olwibulo lwabu nilubaloondakhwo khukhusuubila, khulibabukanania, ne shikhulibalemilia khubikhole biabu shiosishiosi tawe. Buli Omundu alitililwa khushiayakhola."
  52,22,"Ne khulibametela buli imbia yebiamo nende yeyinyama shingala benya."
  52,23,"Balihelesaniamwo efikombe fia okhung’inang’ina filimwo eshinywebwa shibulamwo eshifwabi nohomba tsimbii tawe."
  52,24,"Ne Abakholi babu balibabotokhananga, bang’inang’ina opara mbu bo nebisole bifunikhwe obulai mufikombe fyokhung’inang’ina."
  52,25,"Ne balihengana nibareebananga."
  52,26,"Baliboola mbu: “Toto efwe khwali khale nabandu befu nikhwaria muno."
  52,27,"Mana Nyasaye nakhukhonya, nakhuhonia okhurulana nende eshinyasio shiomulilo omululu."
  52,28,"Toto efwe khwamulamanga (khushialo) Ye yenyene butswa. Toto ye niye Omulayi muno, wetsimbabasi muno.”"
  52,29,"Kho yitsulisia, ne khumikabo chia Nyasaye wuwo sholi Omulosi nohomba Omulalu tawe."
  52,30,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “Uno ni omukaasia wamashairi, wakhulindanga lifwa limuulile.”"
  52,31,"Boola mbu: “Yiisiriesa lifwa, toto esie siesi endi halala ninanyu mukhulindilisia kalibanyola okhurulana nende eshinyasio shia Nyasaye.”"
  52,32,"Nohomba amaparo kabu niko kabarumanga kario, nohomba bo ni Abandu abafuru butswa?"
  52,33,"Nohomba baboolanga mbu: “Wakasia kano (Ikurani)”, halali bo shibasuubilangasa tawe!"
  52,34,"Mana barerekhwo amakhuwa shinga kano, nikali mbu baboolanga akatoto."
  52,35,"Nohomba shibaalongwakhwo nende shiosishiosi tawe, nohomba bo nibo baloonganga (kata nibelonga abeene)?"
  52,36,"Koo! Nibo baloonga likulu nende eshialo? Halali babula obulaamba tawe."
  52,37,"Nohomba bali nende libishilo lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, nohomba nibo abemeli ba buli eshindu?"
  52,38,"Nohomba bali netsingasi tsiokhurechelesiliakhwo? Mana omurechelesi wabu oyo arerekhwo ebifune bilolekha."
  52,39,"Nohomba Nyasaye ali nabakhana nanyu muli nabasiani?"
  52,40,"Nohomba obarebanga bakhurunge, nabo balolanga obusiro muno okhurunga omurungo oko?"
  52,41,"Nohomba bamanyile akefisa mana bakahandikanga?"
  52,42,"Nohomba benyanga okhukhukholela ebifwanga? Halali balia bakhaya nibo abalakholelwa ebifwanga."
  52,43,"Nohomba bali nende nyasaye wundi owulali Nyasaye tawe? Nyasaye nomutswenufu ehale nende bia bamutsokasinjia ninabio."
  52,44,"Ne nibalolanga lileesi lieshinyasio nilikwa okhurula hekulu, bakhaboolele mbu ni amalesi kachingane."
  52,45,"Kho baleshe butswa okhuula olwa balibukaana nende inyanga yabu yabalisishilibwamo."
  52,46,"Inyanga ya ebifwanga biabu shibikhabakhoonye shiosishiosi tawe, ne shibalihabinwa tawe."
  52,47,"Ne toto balia abakhola amabii, balinyoola eshinyasio shindi shilali shino tawe. Ne abaanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  52,48,"Ne linda okhubusia omuse khwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Toto ewe oli mutsimoni tsiefu, ne mutswenule khulwokhumwitsomia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olwa oba niwema."
  52,49,"Ne eshilo khandi omutswenule nende olwa tsing’ining’ini tsitsia."
